04:21.750 --> 04:24.750
By my, uh, crickto-calculations,

04:24.833 --> 04:28.291
the scale of bug arguing
has just reached level ten.

04:28.375 --> 04:31.166
Extreme botheration.

04:31.250 --> 04:35.041
Look, no one will play with anyone.

04:41.458 --> 04:43.625
Problem identified.

04:44.250 --> 04:47.416
Friends arguing over where to play.

04:47.500 --> 04:50.333
No home is perfect. Solution?

04:52.416 --> 04:55.916
I know. We need a new place.

04:56.000 --> 05:00.458
A place that isn't anyone's
because it's everyone's.

05:00.541 --> 05:02.708
But where could that--?

05:02.791 --> 05:04.208
Ooh!

05:06.333 --> 05:07.750
Yes!

05:07.833 --> 05:11.333
A house in a tree.

05:11.416 --> 05:16.791
A tree house,
where we can all come together and play.

05:16.875 --> 05:18.208
Uh...

05:18.291 --> 05:20.416
