05:20.500 --> 05:26.083
How do I, uh, bring arguing friends
together to build this?

05:47.958 --> 05:51.750
Draw it and they will come, I hope.

05:51.833 --> 05:55.916
-What you doing, Cricks?
-Just designing a tree house.

05:56.750 --> 06:00.125
