06:13.916 --> 06:16.500
Sure. I'll get some from Doris.

06:16.583 --> 06:19.291
Boink!

06:19.375 --> 06:23.541
-What's she so excited about?
-I'm designing a tree house.

06:23.625 --> 06:27.000
A tree house? Okay.
You know what it really needs?

06:27.083 --> 06:30.666
A deck where you could sit out
and read, like this.

06:30.750 --> 06:34.958
