more twigs and supports.

06:35.708 --> 06:37.750
I can get all that.

06:37.833 --> 06:40.666
So, what's this tree house thing? Oh!

06:40.750 --> 06:44.375
You know what would make it cool?
A slide. A cool slide.

06:44.458 --> 06:48.500
Okay. But we'll need
some cardboard tubes and--

06:48.583 --> 06:52.166
-Oh, I know where to get those.
-Why do bugs keep coming in here?

06:52.250 --> 06:54.375
Oh, I'm planning a tree house.

06:54.458 --> 06:56.083
Hmm. Not bad.

06:56.708 --> 07:02.958
Oh, but it would be so much better
with an elevator, like... like so.

07:03.041 --> 07:06.458
