13:42.333 --> 13:43.541
Chin up, young bug.

13:43.625 --> 13:47.625
Remember, long as you bounce,
it always counts.

13:49.583 --> 13:53.500
Uh, Kumi, something's wrong
with your head sticks.

13:56.208 --> 13:58.958
This always happens
when the weather's about to change.

14:01.083 --> 14:04.500
You're saying that they are capable
of predicting the weather?

14:04.583 --> 14:07.583
Yes, and it's really annoying.

14:07.666 --> 14:12.791
It's about to... rain!

14:15.291 --> 14:18.791
Guys, we'd better get inside.
It's gonna pour.

