today will remain perfectly sunny.

14:26.250 --> 14:27.500
Uh-oh.

14:39.416 --> 14:42.291
See you, Boris!

14:42.375 --> 14:46.333
Man, some folks just can't handle the wet.

14:49.875 --> 14:53.375
