15:20.500 --> 15:23.500
Okay, Buzz, one, two...

15:24.708 --> 15:26.291
Ta-da!

15:26.375 --> 15:27.791
Ouchie.

15:27.875 --> 15:30.041
Told you. Outdoor game.

15:31.250 --> 15:32.875
