What are you doing?

15:32.958 --> 15:37.250
Wishing. Wishing to stop the rain
so we can play outside.

15:37.333 --> 15:38.750
Good idea, Buzz.

15:38.833 --> 15:42.625
Or we could, like,
tie the grass tops together.

15:42.708 --> 15:45.125
Oh, yeah, to make a roof for the village.

15:45.208 --> 15:49.750
What we need is a magical slug sun dance.

15:49.833 --> 15:52.125
A magic dance?

15:54.083 --> 15:56.416
I've got a way better idea than that.

15:56.500 --> 15:58.500
I mean, Crick has.

15:58.583 --> 16:01.166
We're totally gonna stop the rain first.

16:01.250 --> 16:03.375
Yeah, sure. Right after I do.

16:03.458 --> 16:06.833
Ha! My magic sun dance will beat you all.

16:06.916 --> 16:08.541
We're so going to win.

16:08.625 --> 16:10.000
You so aren't.

16:13.083 --> 16:15.958
Fighting won't stop the rain.

16:16.041 --> 16:19.666
Hey, you, sun, go no way.

16:19.750 --> 16:23.041
Rain, shoo, away.
Go again, hey, go, go.

16:23.125 --> 16:27.291
Join me, Buzz.
The louder it is, the better it works.

16:28.250 --> 16:33.000
