-Yuck, that's great!

17:12.833 --> 17:18.290
Uh, thanks. But yuck usually means
horrible or disgusting.

17:19.250 --> 17:20.458
Oh.

17:27.790 --> 17:31.041
-Yuck?
-Now you're getting it.

17:31.583 --> 17:35.500
