throwing technology,

17:35.583 --> 17:40.458
the cloud catcher will send
the large silk net over the clouds,

17:40.541 --> 17:42.291
-trapping them.
-Awesome!

17:42.375 --> 17:45.166
Then we winch them
carefully to the ground.

17:45.250 --> 17:47.041
Rain stop. Thanks to my--

17:47.125 --> 17:51.083
-I mean, our brilliant idea.
-You guys think the smartest.

17:57.375 --> 17:58.916
You'd better step back.

17:59.000 --> 18:03.666
Once I release this crank,
the cloud catcher will spin quite fast.

18:04.000 --> 18:05.208
Ooh!

18:12.416 --> 18:14.791
Squishee!

18:16.833 --> 18:19.625
Quick, Jay. Reel her in!

18:25.708 --> 18:28.875
Yuck. The yuckiest.

18:28.958 --> 18:32.416
Yeah, all right.
That's the spot right there.

18:32.500 --> 18:34.125
Get down, Brother Boris.

18:36.750 --> 18:38.666
Get down, little sister!

18:47.125 --> 18:48.958
Huh?

18:49.041 --> 18:51.666
