-Hey, young sister.

18:51.750 --> 18:52.916
Didn't see you there.

18:53.000 --> 18:55.708
So, where are all the other
bug brothers and sisters?

18:55.791 --> 18:59.041
They're trying to stop the rain.

18:59.125 --> 19:01.666
